lows you to access and analyze the sample data directly via the cloud anytime, anywhere. Also the data can be shared based on the account privilege.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Sequence data management<br /></strong>Users may upload the sample generation list in the format of bam/vcf, and manage the samples by different types. Besides, it can generate annotation for the variation position of the sample using VEP, which facilitates further screening and analysis of the important hotspots.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Built-in and custom gene &amp; hotspot list<br /></strong>The built-in gene &amp; hotspot list related to the diseases can immediately screen whether the variation loci of different samples are within the list, and further analyze the correlation between the samples and diseases. Moreover, the user can build the gene &amp; hotspot list for the specific diseases.With the built-in gene &amp; hotspot list, it may locate the loci related to specific diseases.Users may build the gene list for specific disease as necessary.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Multi-sample comparison<br /></strong>Based on different scenarios (Trio, Case-control, Family-based analysis, etc.), it may set the comparison layers for different samples, so as to easily search key variation position.</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Report generation<br /></strong>Based on different analysis procedure and screening results provided by the system, automatic report generation and downloading can be done.&nbsp;</li>\n</ul>','','','',0,'',0,0),(1,2,707527454071602171,707527717754126505,0,'H','','<img src=\"/UpFiles/2/Messagess00_Pics707527454071602171/科學研究_定序流程_eng.png\" alt=\" \" />','','','',0,'',0,0),(1,2,707527454037177231,707527717703702223,0,'T','For Genetic Testing Workflow','','','','',0,'',0,0),(2,2,707527454037177231,707527717703702223,0,'H','','<img src=\"/UpFiles/2/Messagess00_Pics707527454037177231/基因檢測流程_eng2.png\" alt=\" \" /><br />\n<ul>\n<li>&nbsp;<span class=\"font_bold\">