)<br /></strong>使用者可以上傳格式為bam/vcf的樣品産生列表，並可將樣品分類管理。此外可使用VEP對樣品變異點位産生註解，以利於進一步篩選分析重要點位。</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>內建與客製化基因及點位列表</strong><strong> (Custom gene &amp; hotspot list)<br /></strong>內建疾病相關之基因列表或點位列表，於不同的使用者樣品中可以快速篩選出發生變異位點是否落於列表之內，進而分析樣品和疾病之間的關係。此外使用者可以建立特定疾病的基因列表或點位列表。可使用內建熱點基因列表找出與特定疾病相關的位點。可自己建立有興趣的特定疾病基因列表。</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>多種樣品比較</strong><strong> (Multi-sample comparison)<br /></strong>可根據不同情境 (Trio, Case-control, Family-based analysis,&hellip;etc) 設置不同樣品比較階層，找尋重要變異點位。</li>\n</ul>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>報告產出</strong><strong> (Report generation)<br /></strong>根據系統提供不同的分析流程及篩選結果，可以提供下載及自動生成報告。</li>\n</ul>','','','',0,'',0,0),(1,2,707526347757402673,707531032503741546,0,'H','','<div class=\"tl\">Transcriptomics is the study of the totality of the gene transcription and the transcriptional regulation laws in the cell. In a broad sense, the transcriptome refers to the set of all transcripts in the cell under certain physiological conditions. In a narrow sense, it refers to the set of all mRNAs. The transcriptome links the genome inherited message with the biological functions. And transcriptome research has become an optimal tool to reveal the regulation of bio growth and development, the stress-resistance adaptation mechanism, biological evolution laws, important mechanisms for disease development and the key molecular targets for regulating the disease gene. In recent years, with the continuous reduction of sequencing cost and increase of sequence output, NGS technologies gradually became an indispensable tool for resolving biological problems with its remarkable advantages such as high accuracy, high throughput, high sensitivity and low operation cost.</div>\n<div class=\"tl\">Transcriptome sequencing can obtain almost all transcripts and gene sequences of a specific cell or organization of a certain species under a certain status. It can be applied to research gene structure, gene function, alternative splicing and new transcript prediction. Compared with the traditional microarray, transcriptome sequencing can test the overall transcription activities of any species without designing the probe for the known sequence. Not only can it provide quantification signal with high accuracy, but also has the features of high throughput and high sensitivity, which is a powerful tool for in-depth research on transcriptome. Currently, transcriptome sequencing has been widely applied in screening the high-quality genes for animals and plants, as well as disease treatment. Yourgene takes advantage of the standardized experimental procedure, advanced test platform and professional information analysis to build the leading transcriptome sequencing base in Taiwan. The highly efficient and excellent quality tech service has earned a good reputation among professionals.</div>\n<div class=\"tl\"><img src=\"/UpFiles/2/Messagess00_Pics707526347757402673/RNA.png\" alt=\" \" /></div>\n<div class=\"tc\"><img src=\"/UpFiles/2/Messagess00_Pics707526347757402673/7_RNA_seq8_900.png\" alt=\" \" width=\"981\" height=\"426\" /></div>','','','',0,'',0,0),(9,2,707526347757402673,707531032503741546,0,'H','','<table style=\"border: 3px solid #ffa500; width: 100%;\" border=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"89\">\n<div class=\"tc\" align=\"center\">Sample type</div>\n</td>\n<td width=\"104\">\n<div class=\"tc\" align=\"center\">Application</div>\n</td>\n<td width=\"112\">\n<div class=\"tc\" align=\"center\">Bioinformatics analysis</div>\n</td>\n<td width=\"707\">\n<div class=\"tc\" align=\"center\">Service Solution</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 230px;\" rowspan=\"9\">\n<div align=\"center\">RNA</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 230px;\" rowspan=\"9\">\n<div align=\"center\">RNA sequencing</div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 230px;\" rowspan=\"3\">\n<div align=\"center\">Basic</div>\n</td>\n<td width=\"707\">\n<p>&nbsp;● Quality trim</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"707\">\n<p>&nbsp;●&