',0,0),(9,1,655406000205656404,655407624040323510,0,'H','','<h4>&nbsp;</h4>\n<table border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"2\"><img src=\"/UpFiles/1/Messagess00_Pics655406000205656404/癌症_適用對象_677.png\" alt=\" \" width=\"492\" height=\"245\" /></td>\n<td><br />\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h4>長期抽菸、飲酒與生活不規律者。</h4>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h4>工作壓力大、經常外食者 (食安問題)。</h4>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h4>長期處於汙染、輻射環境中。</h4>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h4>有預防醫學概念者。</h4>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span style=\"font-size: 13px;\">&nbsp;<br /></span>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<h4>可預示受檢者罹患癌症風險之可能性。</h4>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h4>使受檢者從基因層面了解自我健康狀況，輔助健康管理、強化預防醫學。</h4>\n</li>\n<li>\n<h4>了解家族中的遺傳性癌症，避免遺傳性癌症為家族成員帶來健康威脅。</h4>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>','','','',0,'',0,0),(3,2,707526350310726363,707532647572537741,0,'C','Sample Report','<a href=\"\">16s rRNA Metagenomics </a>','','','',0,'L',0,0),(4,2,707526350310726363,707532647572537741,0,'T','Sequencing Strategies','','','','',0,'',0,0),(5,2,707526350310726363,707532647572537741,0,'H','','<table style=\"border: 3px solid #fa8072; width: 100%;\" border=\"3\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"111\">\n<div class=\"tc\">Applications</div>\n</td>\n<td width=\"446\">\n<p>&nbsp;Metagenomics (16S rRNA )</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"111\">\n<div class=\"tc\">Available Platforms</div>\n</td>\n<td width=\"446\">\n<p>&nbsp;* Platforms：Illumina<br />&nbsp;* Read：Paired-End<br />&nbsp;* Read length：250-300pb</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"111\">\n<div class=\"tc\">Throughput/Coverage</div>\n</td>\n<td width=\"446\">\n<p>&nbsp;1 million reads</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td width=\"111\">\n<div class=\"tc\">Limitation</div>\n</td>\n<td width=\"446\">\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>','','','',0,'',0,0),(1,2,707526337417435230,707742114534502676,0,'C','Bill Chang, Ph.D. | Chief Executive Officer','Dr. Bill Chang is the founder and CEO of Yourgene Bioscience. He is responsible for setting the overall strategic plan and providing vision for the company to continue its pace of rapid growth and expansion.\n\nAfter completing his PhD at University of Melbourne, Australia, Dr Chang joined Academia Sinica in 2007 as a research specialist and established the bioinformatics core facility at the Institute of Plant and Microbial Biology.  In 2010, Dr Chang established Yourgene Bioscience to provide NGS and bioinformatics services, and he co-founded Sofiva Genomics in 2012 to provide prenatal genetic testing services. He is now also an Honorary Fellow at the Faculty of Veterinary Science, University of Melbourne.\n\nDr Chang actively present technical results at many international conferences including at The Ion World Tour in Singapore, Thailand and Taiwan.','','','Bill_Chang_376.png',0,'L',0,0),(2,2,707526353750501317,707532650247131575,0,'H','','<table style=\"width: 100%; border: 3px solid #fa8072;\" border=\"3\" rules=\"all\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\">\n<td>\n<div class=\"tc\">&nbsp;Stage</div>\n</td>\n<td>&nbsp;</td>\n<td>Turnaround time</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"2\">\n<div class=\"tc\">&nbsp;Pre-pregnancy</div>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>&nbsp;Preimplantation genetic screening, PGS</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<div class=\"tc\">&nbsp;coming soon</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p>&nbsp;Inherited Disease Genetic Testing</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<div class=\"tc\">14-30 days</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"2\">\n<div class=\"tc\">&nbsp;Prenatal (&gt;10 weeks)</div>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>&nbsp;Non-Invasive Prenatal Test (NIPT)</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<div class=\"tc\">14 days</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p>&nbsp;Non-Invasive Prenatal Test - Microdeletion (NIPT+)</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<div class=\"tc\">14 day&nbsp;</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td rowspan=\"4\">\n<div class=\"tc\">&nbsp;Adult</div>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>&nbsp;Inherited&nbsp;Cancer&nbsp;Genetic Testing</p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<div class=\"tc\">14-30 days</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p>&nbsp;Cardiomyo