R area and post-PCR area. The experimental facilities of post-PCR are prohibited from going back to pre- PCR, so as to reduce the possibility of cross contamination.\n\nThe experimental process uses a filter tip to avoid cross contamination between samples.\n\nThe instruments used in the experiment, including the PCR machine, various pipets and refrigerators, are calibrated by a TAF certified laboratory periodically on a yearly basis, so as to guarantee stable quality of the experiments. ','','','實驗室區域規劃_s.png',0,'L',0,0),(3,2,707526341114115136,707533745155534033,0,'H','','<table style=\"width: 100%;\" border=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 400px;\">\n<h3>&nbsp;</h3>\n</td>\n<td>&nbsp;\n<h3>Ion S5&trade;&nbsp;</h3>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 400px;\"><img src=\"/UpFiles/2/Messagess00_Pics707526341114115136/Ion_S5_1_2015_11_500322.png\" alt=\" \" /><br /><br /><br /><img src=\"/UpFiles/2/Messagess00_Pics707526341114115136/Ion_S5_2015_11.png\" alt=\" \" width=\"461\" height=\"332\" /></td>\n<td>\n<p><strong>Ion Torrent develops the latest generation of sequencing instrument, Ion S5, which has the following five major sequencing features:</strong></p>\n<p><strong>1.</strong>&nbsp;<strong>Simplicity</strong>: The agents and consumables required for sequencing are simplified and integrated. Working with the Ion Chef&trade; system, it requires less than an hour to finish all operations on the machine.</p>\n<p><strong>2.</strong>&nbsp;<strong>Scalability</strong>: This system provides flexible options. Based on the needed data amount, you may choose three types of customized sequencing chip. In addition, it provides various sequencing types to meet the customer&rsquo;s demands (Medical care: cancer detection, inherited and infectious diseases, and chromosome anomaly).</p>\n<p><strong>3.</strong>&nbsp;<strong>Speed</strong>: Each sequencing takes about 2.5~4 hours. It takes less than one day from DNA to sequence interpretation.</p>\n<p><strong>4. Small sample input:&nbsp;</strong>Since sample types from complicated sources may be of poor quality or incur small degradation sometimes, the minimum DNA or RNA sample amount tolerant to the system is 10 ng for special cases. At the same time, it combines with AmpliSeq&rsquo;s technology to meet the sequencing requirements of small sample inputs.</p>\n<p><strong>5.</strong>&nbsp;<strong>Simple data analysis and storage</strong>:It provides basic analysis (including: machine operation plan design, sequencing result monitoring, and analysis software selection), and advanced analysis (including: data integration, sequencing result notes, marks of sequence variation degree). As for the sequencing data storage, it provides a secure space for storage/access.&nbsp;</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>','','','',0,'',0,0),(1,1,655415416650740222,655416673125454074,0,'H','','<div class=\"tr\"><a href=\"#tab4\">Illumina HiSeq2500</a>│&nbsp;<a href=\"#tab8\">Ion Proton</a>│&nbsp;<a href=\"#tab11\">Ion PGM</a>│&nbsp;<a href=\"#tab15\">Ion S5<br /><br /><img src=\"/UpFiles/1/Messagess00_Pics655415416650740222/sequencing_workflow_中_定序1.png\" alt=\" \" /></a></div>','','','',0,'',0,0),(4,2,707526347320646010,707532640567635300,0,'C','Applications','<ul style=\"list-style-type:square;\"><li>Inherited variation between individuals or populations, such as: genomic difference between different species.<li>Research on the pathogenesis of specific diseases, such as: the variation position of the disease gene.</li>','','','',0,'L',0,0),(5,2,707526347320646010,707532640567635300,0,'C','Sample Report','<a href=\"http://www.yourgene.com.tw/demo/whole-genome/analysis_report.htm\" target=\"_blank\">Human Genome Sequencing</a>\n<a href=\"http://www.yourgene.com.tw/demo/Exome/analysis_report.htm\" target=\"_blank\">Whole-Exome Sequencing</a>\n<a href=\"http://www.yourgene.com.tw/demo/target-seq/analysis_report.htm\" target=\"_blank\">Targeted Sequencing</a>\nYourgene provide Cloud-based NGS Plat